flowchart TB
    A[Main branch] -->|scheduled refresh| B[Transition branch]
    B --> C[Render dbt/Jinja SQL]
    C --> D[Validate translated SQL]
    D --> E[Check dbt config keys]
    E --> F[Check model dependencies]
    F --> G[Compile/build on Trino target]
